NK009(ta)001:0: rdo rje phur pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dum bu bzhugs so //
NK009(ta)001:2: badz+ra k+ai la ya m+au la tan+t+ra khan+da /
NK009(ta)001:4: rdo rje phur pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dum bu /
NK009(ta)001:5: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK009(ta)001:6: rdo rje khro bos zhe sdang gcod //
NK009(ta)001:7: mtshon chen sngon po cher 'bar ba //
NK009(ta)001:8: nam mkha'i dkyil du thig le shar //
NK009(ta)001:9: srog gi sgo ru shar ba dang //
NK009(ta)001:10: snying gi dkyil du bsgom par bya //
NK009(ta)001:11: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)001:12: bsad cing mnan pa nyid min te //
NK009(ta)001:13: phung po'i rdo rje'i bdag nyid de //
NK009(ta)001:14: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK009(ta)001:15: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+n+aana bam h+aum phata /
NK009(ta)001:16: d+aip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK009(ta)001:17: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK009(ta)001:18: 'khor ba rdo rjer sgrub par mdzod //
NK009(ta)001:19: 'khor ba rdo rje phur ba'i lha //
NK009(ta)001:20: ye shes khro bo grub par mdzod //
NK009(ta)001:21: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK009(ta)001:22: rdo rje'i de nyid rang bzhin las //
NK009(ta)001:23: chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK009(ta)001:24: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pas //
NK009(ta)001:25: sku yi gter du bdag skyed cig /
NK009(ta)001:26: thabs kyi spyod pas sems can don //
NK009(ta)001:27: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK009(ta)001:28: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs par mdzod //
NK009(ta)001:29: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsol cig /
NK009(ta)001:30: badz+ra krod+ha h'u ka ra h'u /
NK009(ta)001:32: badz+ra kro d+hi d+ai pa ya ti h'u /
NK009(ta)001:33: badz+ra su kha ra mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:34: badz+ra i shu pa mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:35: 'di ni khro bo chen po h'u mdzad dang /
NK009(ta)001:36: rdo rje lha mo sgra 'byin dang /
NK009(ta)001:37: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma phag gi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:39: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u /
NK009(ta)001:40: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:41: badz+ra kro d+h+ai la s+ya ki h'u /
NK009(ta)001:42: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:43: badz+ra gri d+h+ra mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:44: 'di ni khro bo chen po rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK009(ta)001:45: rdo rje lha mo sgeg mo dang /
NK009(ta)001:46: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma stag gi mgo bo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:47: bya rgod kyi mgo can no //
NK009(ta)001:48: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h'u /
NK009(ta)001:49: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:50: badz+ra kro d+hi t+ai t+aa ru h'u /
NK009(ta)001:51: badz+ra ts+aa ma ra mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:52: badz+ra t+aa na mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:53: 'di ni khro bo dbyug sngon 'chang ba dang /
NK009(ta)001:54: lha mo rdo rje sder mo dang /
NK009(ta)001:55: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma g.yag mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:57: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h'u /
NK009(ta)001:58: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:59: badz+ra kro d+hi sh+ma sh+aa na pa ti h'u /
NK009(ta)001:60: badz+ra ha ri na mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:61: badz+ra u lu ka mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:62: 'di na khro bo gshin rje mthar byed dang /
NK009(ta)001:63: rdo rje lha mo dur khrod kyi bdag mo dang /
NK009(ta)001:64: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma ri dwags kyi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:66: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK009(ta)001:68: badz+ra kro d+hi mu ha la h'u /
NK009(ta)001:69: badz+ra t+ya ki mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:70: badz+ra pre ta mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:71: 'di ni khro bo mi g.yo mgon po dang /
NK009(ta)001:72: rdo rje lha mo gtun khung ma dang /
NK009(ta)001:73: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma gzig gi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:75: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai ba h'u /
NK009(ta)001:76: hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:77: badz+ra kro d+hi dza ya ti h'u /
NK009(ta)001:78: badz+ra bi t+aa la mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:79: badz+ra pak+shi ta mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:80: 'di ni khro bo rta mgrin dang /
NK009(ta)001:81: rdo rje lha mo gtum mo dang /
NK009(ta)001:82: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma byi la'i mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:83: bu shud kyi mgo can no //
NK009(ta)001:84: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h'u /
NK009(ta)001:86: badz+ra kro d+hi ba bya ti h'u /
NK009(ta)001:87: badz+ra sri ga la mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:88: badz+ra pany+tsa ra na mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:89: 'di ni khro bo gzhan gyis mi thub pa dang /
NK009(ta)001:90: rdo rje lha mo mda' snyems ma dang /
NK009(ta)001:91: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma spyang ku'i mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:93: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ka kun+da li h'u /
NK009(ta)001:95: badz+ra kro d+hi sa bya mi ti h'u /
NK009(ta)001:96: badz+ra sim ha mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:97: badz+ra ti ti la mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:98: 'di ni khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK009(ta)001:99: rdo rje lha mo sgra mdzad ma /
NK009(ta)001:100: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma seng ge'i mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:101: pha wam gi mgo can no //
NK009(ta)001:102: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lo kya bi dza ya h'u /
NK009(ta)001:104: badz+ra kro d+hi m+aa ra ya h'u /
NK009(ta)001:105: badz+ra rak+shi sa mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:106: badz+ra na ku la mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:107: 'di ni khro bo 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK009(ta)001:108: rdo rje lha mo gsod byed ma dang /
NK009(ta)001:109: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma dred kyi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:111: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK009(ta)001:112: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:113: badz+ra kro d+hi mun+de mam h'u /
NK009(ta)001:114: badz+ra rak+sha sa mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)001:115: badz+ra ka shi ka mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)001:116: 'di ni khro bo stobs po che dang /
NK009(ta)001:117: rdo rje lha mo rigs byed ma dang /
NK009(ta)001:118: sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma dom gyi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:120: badz+ra yak+sha sa da h'u dzah badz+ra b+hee ra be h'u h'u /
NK009(ta)001:122: badz+ra ma ra ni h'u hoh 'di ni shar du pu shud kyi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:123: lhor bya rog gi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:124: nub tu srin bya'i mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)001:125: byang du khra'i mgo can no //
NK009(ta)001:126: 'khor ba phur bu bsgrub don du //
NK009(ta)001:127: dbang dang byin rlabs zhu ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)001:128: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK009(ta)001:129: ye shes khro bo gshegs nas kyang //
NK009(ta)001:130: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK009(ta)001:131: phur pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK009(ta)001:132: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)001:133: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)001:134: pho nya chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)001:135: bdag nyid chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)001:136: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)001:137: khyi yi gdong can dus la bab //
NK009(ta)001:138: bsgral bar bya ba'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)001:139: byang chub tu ni sems bskyed nas //
NK009(ta)001:140: dus gsum sangs rgyas sras bzhin du //
NK009(ta)001:141: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK009(ta)001:142: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang 'gegs //
NK009(ta)001:143: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK009(ta)001:144: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK009(ta)001:145: yud tsam gyis ni de bkug nas //
NK009(ta)001:146: mngon spyod tshul gyis bsgral ba dang //
NK009(ta)001:147: lus ngag phye mar mdzad nas kyang //
NK009(ta)001:148: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK009(ta)001:152: h+r+aihsh+tihbi kri ta badz+ra h'u ka ra h'u /
NK009(ta)001:153: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh sarba big+h+n+aana badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:154: bgegs byed pa yi bdud rnams dang //
NK009(ta)001:155: sdug bsngal sems la mnyam sbyor ba //
NK009(ta)001:156: che ge mo zhes bya ba'i bdud //
NK009(ta)001:157: zungs shig rdungs shig rnam par chings //
NK009(ta)001:158: gtogs shig grogs dang dbye bar gyis //
NK009(ta)001:159: ring nas khug la smra ru chug /
NK009(ta)001:160: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK009(ta)001:161: bdag gis dbang du byas gyur nas //
NK009(ta)001:162: bsgo ba'i bka' nyan gus par gyis //
NK009(ta)001:163: h'u pa ra bid+y+aa tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:165: gri h+na gri h+na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:167: t+r+aa sha ya t+r+aa sha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:168: ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+r+aihdan+da h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:169: sh+r+ai g+h+ram a n+aa ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:171: dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:172: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:173: bin+d+ha ya bin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:174: pho nya bran dang mngag pa'i tshogs //
NK009(ta)001:175: khyod kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK009(ta)001:176: mngon spyod ji ltar nges pa dang //
NK009(ta)001:177: mngon spyod byin rlabs de bzhin mdzod //
NK009(ta)001:187: a dzi te a pa ra dzi te /
NK009(ta)001:188: m+aa ra se na pra mar+d+ha ni h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:189: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' lung gis //
NK009(ta)001:190: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK009(ta)001:191: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK009(ta)001:192: mgo bo tshal pa brgya ru gyis //
NK009(ta)001:193: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren rnams //
NK009(ta)001:194: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK009(ta)001:195: h'u ma ma pa sh+aam ku ru /
NK009(ta)001:196: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK009(ta)001:197: sod cig lha min lha yang rung //
NK009(ta)001:198: nga la bar chod byed pa'i bdud //
NK009(ta)001:199: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par mdzod //
NK009(ta)001:201: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)001:202: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK009(ta)001:203: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK009(ta)001:204: rdo rje me yis snying bsregs nas //
NK009(ta)001:205: lus sems rdul bzhin brlag par mdzod //
NK009(ta)001:206: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK009(ta)001:207: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NK009(ta)001:208: lha yang rung ste bsgral bar bya /
NK009(ta)001:209: kha tam kha tam kha tam /
NK009(ta)001:212: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK009(ta)001:216: gsang sngags kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis byin gyis brlabs so //
NK009(ta)001:217: sangs rgyas kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis mthun 'gyur ro //
NK009(ta)001:218: brnag pa de kho na nyid do //
NK009(ta)001:219: k+ai la ya lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas so //
NK009(ta)001:220: k+ai la ya bco brgyad bzlas nas snying dkar nag gi mtshams su'o //
NK009(ta)001:222: ho ho hoh phata phata phata /
NK009(ta)001:224: rdo rje phur pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dum bu /
NK009(ta)001:225: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas dngos kyi rgya dpe dang mthun par dpal ldan sa skya pan+di tas /
NK009(ta)001:227: shangs kyi sreg shing du bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa /
NK009(ta)001:228: gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi phyogs la lo ts+aa ba
NK009(ta)001:229: 'gos dang chag sogs kha cig gis the tshom du
NK009(ta)001:230: mdzad pa na / 'brog mi lo chen gyis rdo
NK009(ta)001:231: rje gdan gyi sgo gong du ru lu 'bru brgyad
NK009(ta)001:233: pan+di ta 'ga' zhig gi phyag dpe'i gseb tu yang
NK009(ta)001:234: phur gyi rgyud kyi dum bu 'dra gzigs kyang man
NK009(ta)001:236: de la dpags na snga 'gyur rgyud sde'i snying po
NK009(ta)001:237: rnams phyis pan grub rnams kyis shin tu gsang ba'i
NK009(ta)001:238: yi dam du mdzad par mngon ces mkhas pa dag
NK009(ta)001:240: khyad par kha che'i ma h+aa pan+di ta sh+aakya sh+r+ai
NK009(ta)001:241: la slob dpon chen pos dngos su gnang ba'i yang
NK009(ta)001:242: dag me gcig gi gdams pa lo ts+aa ba rab
NK009(ta)001:243: mchog dpal gyis bsgyur ba dang /
NK009(ta)001:244: 'jam mgon sa skya pan+di ta shangs sreg shing gi dgon par bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK009(ta)001:245: sngags pa zhig gis rgya dpe zhig phul ba la gzigs pa na /
NK009(ta)001:246: phur ba rtsa ba'i dum bu slob dpon rin po che'i phyag dpe 'khrul med yin par dgongs te /
NK009(ta)001:247: yid bzhin gyi nor bu 'di lta bu rnyed pa ni shin tu skal pa bzang bas /
NK009(ta)001:248: khyed rang ri gdong ma gir dpe cha bsnams la bzhugs shig /
NK009(ta)001:249: nged cag gis bsu ba byed pa yin no gsungs
NK009(ta)001:250: te rje nyid kyi gtsos mdzad pa'i 'dus pa rgya
NK009(ta)001:251: mtshos mchod pa'i sprin chen po dang bcas te bsu
NK009(ta)001:252: ba'i bkod pa rgyas par mdzad de /
NK009(ta)001:253: de nyid du rang 'gyur gnang ba sogs la brten nas /
NK009(ta)001:254: snga 'gyur la klan ka byed pa rnams kyi sar yang /
NK009(ta)001:256: rdo rje phur pa'i chos ni rtsod med nyi zla
NK009(ta)001:257: lta bu'o zhes grags pas phrin las rgya cher 'phel
NK009(ta)001:258: ba'i bdag po'i rkyen phun sum tshogs par gyur to
